      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really solid shape, perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It runs beautifully and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road with you today! I\u2019ve taken great care of it and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to chat!",
      "price": 29500.0,
