      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera features the naturally aspirated 3.6L M96/05 flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed G97 manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut with recently refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the communicative feedback of the hydraulic steering rack. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an LN Engineering IMS retrofit and a new Rear Main Seal (RMS). The engine exhibits strong compression across all cylinders with no evidence of bore scoring. Finished in Arctic Silver over a Black leather interior, the car shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited road use. It sits on 19-inch Carrera S 'Lobster Fork' alloys wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber, providing exceptional lateral grip and turn-in response.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
